MethodDef.Name: Derivation of the variable ACAT1 from the domain ADCM

Description.TranslatedText: If SDG02NAM ^= ' ' or CDG02NAM ^= ' ' or CDG05NAM ^= ' ' or CDG06NAM ^= ' or (SDG01NAM ^= ' ' and .<CMENDY-CMSTDY+1<14 ) then ACAT1 = 'Category 1'; else if CDG01NAM ^= ' ' or CDG03NAM ^= ' ' or CDG04NAM ^= ' or CDG07NAM ^= ' ' or CDG08NAM ^= ' ' or CDG09NAM ^= ' or CDG10NAM ^= ' ' or CDG11NAM ^= ' ' or CDG12NAM ^= ' or (SDG01NAM ^= ' ' and CMENDY-CMSTDY+1>=14 ) then ACAT1 = 'Category 2'; else if CDG13NAM ^= ' ' then ACAT1 = 'Category 3'.

MethodDef.Name: Derivation of the variable ADYSOP from the domain ADRC

Description.TranslatedText: If AONG = "Y" then ADYSOP=CEENDTC - LSTDDT + ADYSSP - 8 + 1; Else ADYSOP=ADYSSP.

MethodDef.Name: Derivation of the variable ADYSOPG from the domain ADRC

Description.TranslatedText: If 2 <= ADYSOP <= 3 then put "1-3 days"; Else if 4 <= ADYSOP <= 7 then put "4-7 days"; Else if 8 <= ADYSOP then put "8 days or more"; else if CEENDTC is missing or partially missing then put "Missing end date"; Else if ADYSOP is missing then put missing.

MethodDef.Name: Derivation of the variable ADYSSP from the domain ADRC

Description.TranslatedText: If at least one ASEVGDxx = 1 or 2 or 3 then ADYSSP=total number of days with ASEVGDxx >=1; Else if at least one ASEVGDxx=0 then ADYSSP=0; Else if all ASEVGDxx are missing then ADYSSP is missing. Note: xx=00-07.

MethodDef.Name: Derivation of the variable ADYSSPG from the domain ADRC

Description.TranslatedText: If 1 <= ADYSSP <= 3 then put "1-3 days"; Else if 4 <= ADYSSP <= 7 then put "4-7 days"; Else if ADYSSP=8 then put "8 days"; Else if ADYSSP is missing then put missing.

MethodDef.Name: Derivation of the variable ANL01FL from the domain ADAE

Description.TranslatedText: Y if SAFFL='Y' and ASEVGRN ne 0 and ( ( (ASTDY = . and .<length(AESTDTC)<10 and partial date of AESTDTC <= partial date of (LSTDDT+30)) or AESER="Y" or AEMAAE="Y" or AECAT = 'ADVERSE EVENT OF SPECIAL INTEREST' ) or (1<=ASTDY<=31) or (31<ASTDY and (AESER="Y" or AEMAAE="Y" or AECAT = 'ADVERSE EVENT OF SPECIAL INTEREST') or LSTDDT = . ); else leave null.

MethodDef.Name: Derivation of the variable ANL01FL from the domain ADRC

Description.TranslatedText: ANL01FL = Y if SAFFL='Y' and ADYSSP is not missing and ( (SAF1FL= 'Y' and LSTDOSN = 1) or (SAF2FL = 'Y' and LSTDOSN = 2) or (SAF3FL = 'Y' and LSTDOSN = 3) or (SAF4FL = 'Y' and LSTDOSN = 4) or (SAF5FL = 'Y' and LSTDOSN = 5)); ANL01FL is null otherwise.

MethodDef.Name: Derivation of the variable ANL01RS from the domain ADAE

Description.TranslatedText: If SAFFL="N" then "Excluded from Safety Analysis Set"; else if ASEVGRN=0 then "Reported by investigator but derived as Grade 0"; else if .<AESTDY<1 then "Event started before 1st injection"; else if AESER ne "Y" and AEMAAE ne "Y" and AECAT ne 'ADVERSE EVENT OF SPECIAL INTEREST' and ( ASTDY>31 or (astdy = . and .<length(AESTDTC)<10 and partial date of AESTDTC > partial date of (LSTDDT+30) ) ) then "Day of onset after D30 for non-serious AE/non-AESI/non-MAAE"; else leave null.

MethodDef.Name: Derivation of the variable ANL01RS from the domain ADRC

Description.TranslatedText: If SAFFL = "N" then ANL01RS = "Excluded from Safety Analysis Set"; Else if ADYSSP is missing then ANL01RS = "Derived presence during the solicited period is missing"; Null, otherwise.

MethodDef.Name: Derivation of the variable ANL02FL from the domain ADAE

Description.TranslatedText: Y when: 1. If ANL01FL="Y" and (ASTDY = . and 1<=ASTDY<=8); 2. if ANL01FL ='Y' and ASTDY = . then: (2a) If ADAE.LSTDDT =. Then ANL02FL='Y'; (2b) else if LSTDDT not missing and AE.AESTDTC missed the Date part then: if "Month/Year of AE.AESTDTC" <= "Month/Year of last vaccination date +7 " then ANL02FL='Y'; (2c) else if LSTDDT not missing and AE.AESTDTC missed the Month and Date part then: if "Year of AE.AESTDTC" <= "Year of last vaccination date +7 " then ANL02FL='Y'; else leave the ANL02FL as blank.

MethodDef.Name: Derivation of the variable ANL03FL from the domain ADAE

Description.TranslatedText: Y when: 1. If ANL01FL="Y" and (1<=ASTDY<=31); 2. if ANL01FL ='Y' and ASTDY = . then: (2a) If ADAE.LSTDDT =. Then ANL03FL='Y'; (2b) else if LSTDDT not missing and AE.AESTDTC missed the Date part then: if "Month/Year of AE.AESTDTC" <= "Month/Year of last vaccination date + 30 " then ANL03FL='Y'; (2c) else if LSTDDT not missing and AE.AESTDTC missed the Month and Date part then: if "Year of AE.AESTDTC" <= "Year of last vaccination date +30 " then ANL03FL='Y'; else leave the ANL03FL as blank.

MethodDef.Name: Derivation of the variable ANL04FL from the domain ADAE

Description.TranslatedText: Y when: 1. if AESTDTC is completed: Y if ANL01FL="Y" and ANL03FL ne "Y" and ADSL.TRTEDT+30 < AE.AESTDTC <= ADSL.EOSDT; 2. if AESTDTC has missing Day and non-missing Month and Year: Y if ANL01FL="Y" and ANL03FL ne "Y" and Month/Year of ADSL.TRTEDT+30 < Month/Year of AE.AESTDTC <= Month/Year of ADSL.EOSDT; 3. if AESTDTC has missing Day and Month and non-missing Year: Y if ANL01FL="Y" and ANL03FL ne "Y" and Year of ADSL.TRTEDT+30 < Year of AE.AESTDTC <= Year of ADSL.EOSDT; else leave the ANL04FL as blank.

MethodDef.Name: Derivation of the variable AONG from the domain ADRC

Description.TranslatedText: If ASEVGD07 > 0 and ASEVGD08 > 0, then AONG=Y; Else if ASEVGD07 = 0 or ASEVGD08 = 0, then AONG=N; else AONG is missing.

MethodDef.Name: Derivation of the variable AREL from the domain ADAE

Description.TranslatedText: For AESCAT = 'ADMINISTRATION SITE', AREL="RELATED"; For AESCAT = 'SYSTEMIC', If AEREL in ('RELATED',' ') then AREL = 'RELATED'; else if AERELNST = 'RELATED' then AREL = 'RELATED'; else if AERELNST = ' ' and AESTDTC ge 22APR2020 then AREL = 'RELATED'; otherwise AREL = 'NOT RELATED'.

MethodDef.Name: Derivation of the variable ARELNST from the domain ADAE

Description.TranslatedText: 1.Not missing AE.AERELNST: equal to AE.AERELNST; 2.Missing AE.AERELNST: (2a) Systemic AE: "RELATED" if the start date on or after April 22, 2020; otherwise equal to "NOT RELATED". (2b) ADMINISTRATION SITE AE: "RELATED".

MethodDef.Name: Derivation of the variable ASEVGR from the domain ADAE

Description.TranslatedText: 1. If AE is not listed in the measurable solicited reactions list (see the protocol) then derive from AE.AESEV ("Mild" = "Grade 1", "Moderate" = "Grade 2", "Severe" = "Grade 3"). If AESEV is missing then ASEVGR=" ". 2. Else if the AE is listed in the measurable solicited reactions list (AEDECOD in (INJECTION SITE ERYTHEMA, INJECTION SITE SWELLING, PYREXIA, POST VACCINATION FEVER)), ASEVGR is calculated as defined in the protocol: - For AEDECOD in (INJECTION SITE ERYTHEMA, INJECTION SITE SWELLING), NONE: 0 mm GRADE 1: >0 to <25 mm, GRADE 2: >=25 to <50 mm, GRADE 3: >=50 mm or FAAE.FAORRES="NM"; - For AEDECOD in (PYREXIA, POST VACCINATION FEVER), NONE: <100.4F, GRADE 1: >=100.4F to <=101.3F, GRADE 2: >101.3F to <=103.1F, GRADE 3: >103.1F. If measure is missing then ASEVGR =" ".
